verses.text:
Now, behold, the children of Ammon and Moab and Mount Seir, whom you
would not let Israel invade when they came out of the land of Egypt, but they turned away from them, and
didn’t destroy them;

Then the LORD’s Spirit came on Jahaziel the son of Zechariah,
the son of Benaiah, the son of Jeiel, the son of Mattaniah, the Levite, of the sons of Asaph, in the middle
of the assembly;
